 AeroSpace uses the minimum amount of GUI, I would rather think it's a CLI app, which will usually not follow macOS's tradition but have more similarity with Linux's.\n\nIf we support multiple alternatives for config path, I don't think these concerns would become a issue since we can support them all. And I don't think the order will matter since typically users will only put their configuration at one place and they have to do it manually.","files":null}]}